snippet.title: Patron Alpha Footage
snippet.description:
WISHLIST GAME ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1538570/Patron/

First footage from city building game  Patron. Game introduces SOCIAL dimension: as your city grows, so does your population with all the good and bad it brings - class tensions, social in/justice, immigration, religious strife, protests and even civilian uprisings.
